title: Sam Smith Set To Play 'We Can Survive' Benefit Concert Tonight
text: Sam Smith Set To Play 'We Can Survive' Benefit Concert Tonight Sunday, 25 October 2015 (20 minutes ago) Sam Smith keeps his eyes on the exit door after arriving at LAX airport in Los Angeles on Friday night (October 23). The 23-year-old “Writings On The Wall” singer will be performing at the We Can Survive benefit concert along with The Weeknd, Demi Lovato , Nick Jonas, and more later tonight.
